sequenceDiagram
    participant Entry as 入口脚本
    participant Builder as PipelineBuilder
    participant P as Pipeline
    participant R as Reader
    participant PS as ASTParseStage
    participant SP as SourceParser
    participant ES as DocstringExtractStage
    participant DP as DocstringParser
    participant EN as EnrichStage
    participant ER as Enricher
    participant W as Writer

    Entry->>Builder: build_xxx_pipeline(config)
    Builder-->>P: 管道实例（注入对应策略）
    Entry->>P: run(config)

    P->>R: process(config)
    Note right of R: 读取输入 JSON<br/>加载 .py 源文件
    R-->>P: List[RawSourceFile]

    P->>PS: process(raw_files)
    PS->>SP: parse(raw)
    Note right of SP: ast.parse() 解析源码<br/>TC: 定位 class Test_*<br/>AW: 定位 def aw_*
    SP-->>PS: List[ParsedEntity]
    PS-->>P: List[(RawSourceFile, ParsedEntity)]

    P->>ES: process(parsed_data)
    ES->>DP: parse_docstring(docstring)
    Note right of DP: TC: 提取步骤描述列表<br/>AW: 提取函数功能描述
    DP-->>ES: DocstringStructure
    ES-->>P: List[(RawSourceFile, StructuredEntity)]

    P->>EN: process(structured_data)
    EN->>ER: enrich(raw, structured)
    Note right of ER: TC: FIELD_MAPPING + code_pair_list<br/>AW: function_name + description + code
    ER-->>EN: List[CorpusItem]
    EN-->>P: List[CorpusItem]

    P->>W: process(corpus_items)
    Note right of W: TC: 每个用例一个 JSON<br/>AW: 聚合输出单个 JSON
    W-->>P: 完成

    P-->>Entry: 清洗完成
